title: Can a 3D printed Ukulele Sound Better Than a Wood One?

media:group.media:title: Can a 3D printed Ukulele Sound Better Than a Wood One?
media:group.media:description: A custom instrument is coveted by most musicians. Being able to say you designed and built the instrument...even more so. With the exception of the strings, every single part of this Concert Ukulele is 3D printed and was designed in CAD starting from a blank slate.
